    "description": "Tata Communications Consulting Pvt Ltd has an exciting opening for a Full Stack Developer at our Rajkot office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Tata Communications Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nTata Communications Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in Rust\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n• Proficiency in REST APIs\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Rajkot, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Tata Communications Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
